Product: Clinora

Version: 1.0

Document Type: End-to-End User Journeys & Use Cases

Audience: Product, Frontend, Backend, QA, DevOps, Architecture

1. Purpose

The purpose of this document is to define the complete business workflows performed by every user of the Clinora platform.

Each workflow describes how different users interact with the system from start to finish, including business decisions, validations, exceptions, notifications, and expected outcomes.

This document serves as the foundation for:

UI/UX Design
API Design
Database Design
Sprint Planning
Test Case Preparation
2. Primary Actors
Role	Description
Patient	Books appointments and views health records
Reception	Manages daily clinic operations
Doctor	Provides consultations
Laboratory	Processes diagnostic requests
Clinic Admin	Manages clinic operations
Super Admin	Manages Clinora platform
